text: "Them Bones" is a 1992 song by Alice in Chains. It is the opening track to their second studio album Dirt. It went to number 24 on the Billboard Mainstream Rock chart, number 93 in Australia, number 26 in the United Kingdom and number 22 in Ireland. ==Track listing== ==References== Category:1992 songs Category:Alice in Chains songs
